ore\r\n\r\nBy \'Data*\' I mean files containing personally identifiable data belonging to clients (e.g. ALDAS import files)\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Data* must be used in-situ (i.e. destroyed as soon as there is no direct reason to have that data – this includes destroying the data in any back-ups or archives they may have been copied to)\r\n2. Data* must be checked-in to the register\r\n3. Data* must not be transferred through the Internet on unencrypted channels\r\n4. Data* should be in a set location. If they are copied to another location the file in the original location should be destroyed (except during back-up and archive) unless other users may need access to that file.\r\n5. Data* should be stored on computers that cannot be accessed by unknown third parties\r\n6. Data* on removable media going outside the physical perimeter should be encrypted\r\n7. All media should be made unreadable via software, and where appropriate physically prior to disposal.\r\n8. The Data* can only by used for lawful purposes and as agreed with the client',NULL,NULL,5,6,6,NULL,3,4,'2013-05-23 14:55:38','2013-05-29 14:45:16','2013-05-23',100,NULL,NULL,1096,1,2,0,NULL),(1097,2,6,'Implement encryption of server backups','','2013-07-26',NULL,12,NULL,16,NULL,3,3,'2013-05-28 11:25:04','2015-03-04 12:03:11','2013-05-28',0,10,NULL,1097,1,2,0,NULL),(1098,2,46,'Encrypt all user uploaded files on the server','','2013-07-26',NULL,12,NULL,16,NULL,3,4,'2013-05-28 11:25:43','2015-03-04 15:41:22','2013-05-28',0,10,NULL,1098,1,2,0,NULL),(1099,1,4,'When you put a text filter into the project codes screen (eg. W20) the next page link keeps showing the first page','','2013-07-26',11,11,6,17,109,3,5,'2013-05-28 14:38:57','2015-03-06 16:12:26','2013-05-28',100,0,NULL,1099,1,2,0,NULL),(1100,2,4,'Encrypt all user uploaded files on the server','','2013-07-26',NULL,12,NULL,16,NULL,3,5,'2013-05-29 15:05:24','2015-03-04 15:41:37','2013-05-28',0,10,NULL,1100,1,2,0,NULL),(1101,1,44,'Create SMU data gathering form and re