ent academic year. At the year end when the year of study is incremented a new student history record should be created for the new academic year with the new year of study.\r\nThe only problem is that the year of study could be updated manually using Edit student or through a student import. We would need to work out what to do. I would assume we need to update the year of study on the student history for the current academic year.\r\n\r\nThere would be a problem creating the data for the academic year 2013/2014 though I still have the database dump from before the year end was run which could be used to create the student history records\r\n\r\nThis solution would also solve the problem of including students that are not currently on a course as it does not rely on the group.\r\n\r\nThe Registry Export has a similar issue which can be solved in the same way.','2014-12-03 16:47:44',0),(7738,1346,'Issue',23,'','2014-12-04 20:32:56',0),(7739,1351,'Issue',3,'Please go ahead with this on the basis described','2014-12-08 13:12:05',0),(7740,1351,'Issue',3,NULL,'2014-12-08 13:12:42',0),(7741,1351,'Issue',3,'','2014-12-08 13:14:28',0),(7742,1305,'Issue',3,NULL,'2014-12-08 13:15:00',0),(7743,1351,'Issue',3,NULL,'2014-12-08 13:15:07',0),(7744,1355,'Issue',22,'it has been configured tested on my test laptop by open the site http://192.168.5.100/hellp.php \'Word Hello\'','2014-12-09 14:51:14',0),(7745,855,'Issue',6,'I believe this has been covered by issue #1305 and can now be closed.','2014-12-09 21:06:56',0),(7746,939,'Issue',6,'I believe this has been covered by issue #1305 and can now be closed.','2014-12-09 21:07:47',0),(7747,1111,'Issue',6,'I believe this has been covered by issue #1305 and can now be closed.','2014-12-09 21:08:21',0),(7748,1111,'Issue',3,'','2014-12-10 10:24:28',0),(7749,939,'Issue',3,'','2014-12-10 10:24:55',0),(7750,855,'Issue',3,'','2014-12-10 10:25:17',0),(7751,1355,'Issue',22,'It has been done as well on the Cloudtest server, http://192.168.5.101/h